                                    Ethiopian)</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="grace"><p>ʿĀmata məḥrat (Era of Grace)</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="diocletian"><p>ʿĀmata samāʿtāt (Era of Martyrs (Diocletian))</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="alexander"><p> Era of Alexander</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="evangelists"><p>Evangelists' years</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="islamic"><p>Hiǧrī (Islamic)</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="hijri"><p>Hiǧrī (Islamic) in IslHornAfr</p></calendar><calendar xml:id="julian"><p>Julian</p></calendar></calendarDesc></t:profileDesc>
